messages.message: Happy Monday, quick reminder that this Friday is <#C03UK2BB17X|> and `our code cut for next major release 22.10 is set to be next Tuesday 10/11` right after national holiday on 10/10. This means our UAT period will be shortened by a day so please make plans and arrangements accordingly. :pray:
What time is code cut on 10/11?
we plan to do it by noon 12PM PST so we can make up some UAT time to still be able to deploy to ib.com (http://ib.com) by the following Monday
